的立体声扬声器......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913099/google-pixel-8 -改进的扬声器质量&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913099/google-pixel-8-improved-speaker-quality" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913099/google-pixel-8-improved-speaker-quality</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry></feed>